00:41:37.760 --> 00:41:42.330
It was really, really not
exotic tasting at all.

00:41:42.330 --> 00:41:45.850
So the thing is one of
the ways they preserve it.

00:41:45.850 --> 00:41:47.150
Jellyfish were are watery.

00:41:47.150 --> 00:41:48.450
